          <h2 id="select">Select (Drop Down)</h2>
          <div class="example-box">
            <h3>Simple Drop Down</h3>
            <p>Simple drop downs can be used when finer control of individual options is not needed. The simple type cannot do things like hide or disable items in the list, nor can it set the value attribute of an option to a given value. It does not do any extra functionality.</p>
            <p>When more advanced features are needed, refer to the advanced drop down.</p>
            <h4>Simple Dropdown Example:</h4>
            <%- include("../../partials/form_partials.ejs", {
              "forms": [
                {
                  "type": "select",
                  "config": {
                    "label": "Gender",
                    "hint": "Please select the option closest to how you identify",
                    "id": "",
                    "options": [
                      "Select Your Gender",
                      "Male",
                      "Female",
                      "Other"
                    ]
                  }
                }
              ]
            }); %>
            <h4>Simple Dropdown Code:</h4>
            <pre>
              <code class="language-markup">
                <script type="text/html">
                  <%%- include(partials+"form_partials.ejs", {
                    "forms": [
                      {
                        "type": "select",
                        "config": {
                          "label": "Gender",
                          "hint": "Please select the option closest to how you identify",
                          "id": "",
                          "options": [
                            "Select Your Gender",
                            "Male",
                            "Female",
                            "Other"
                          ]
                        }
                      }
                    ]
                  }); %%>
                </script>
              </code>
            </pre>
            <h4>Simple Dropdown HTML Code:</h4>
            <pre>
              <code class="language-markup">
                <script type="text/html">
                  <div class="form-group">
                    <label for="selectgender" class="uikit-text-input__label">Gender <span class="hint">Please select the option closest to how you identify</span></label>
                    <select name="selectgender" id="selectgender" class="uikit-text-input input-half">
                      <option selected="" value="select_your_gender">Select Your Gender</option>
                      <option value="male">Male</option>
                      <option value="female">Female</option>
                      <option value="other">Other</option>
                    </select>
                  </div>
                </script>
              </code>
            </pre>
